{{Infobox dungeon |name = Team Plasma Assault |image = [[File:Team Plasma Assault.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Team Plasma Assault. |tokens = 241,500 |location = Opelucid City }} '''Team Plasma Assault''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 4,603,000 HP.
